In addition to the utilities associated with the individual
 components of MythOS, additional programs are provided.
 These are outside of the scope of the individual components,
 but provide services which are needed to take full advantage of
 the MythOS collection.
\par

\line{\b\fs28 Features}\par

Bitmap recoloring utility to ensure all images are precolored
 with the run-time {\i Van Gogh} palette.
\par

\line{\b\fs28 Future Work}\par

The Picture Utility will have an interactive mode added in the
 near future.  Other utilities will be added as the need arises.
\par

